{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 11,
  "title": "第十一章（無用）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "三十輻共一轂，"
    },
    {
      "text": "當其無，有車之用。"
    },
    {
      "text": "埏埴以為器，"
    },
    {
      "text": "當其無，有器之用。"
    },
    {
      "text": "鑿戶牖以為室，"
    },
    {
      "text": "當其無有室之用。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故有之以為利，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無之以為用。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "古者車三十輻，法月數也。共一轂者，轂中有孔，故眾輻共湊之。治身者當除情去慾，使五藏空虛，神乃歸之。治國者寡能，摠眾弱共使強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無，謂空虛。轂中空虛，輪得轉行，轝中空虛，人得載其上也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "埏，和也。埴，土也。和土以為飲食之器。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "器中空虛，故得有所盛受。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂作屋室。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言戶牖空虛，人得以出入觀視；室中空虛，人得以居處，是其用。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利，物也，利於形用，器中有物。室中有人，恐其屋破壞，腹中有神，畏其形亡也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言虛空者乃可用盛受萬物，故曰虛無能制有形。道者空也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
